text: This is a summary of the electoral history of Saeed Jalili, an Iranian Principlist politician who was Secretary of the Supreme National Security Council (2007–2013). == Parliamentary elections == === 2004 === He ran from Mashhad and lost. === 2008 === He ran from Mashhad and lost. == Presidential election == === 2013 === == References == Category:Electoral history of Iranian politicians
title: Electoral history of Saeed Jalili
